echo  "Please examine (and modify if necessary) the Xsession, Xclients, and"
echo  "wdm-config files in the wdm config directory (by default: /usr/local/etc/wdm)." 
echo  "Also, NOTE that the Xsession and Xclients (or ~./Xclients) files MUST be marked"
echo  "executable.  These files are the shell files which actually create"
echo  "the user's environment and start the window manager.  In addition, there"
echo  "can be a ~/.xsession or a ~/.Xclients file for each user"
echo  "in which case these files are executed (and MUST be marked executable)."
